Package: isoexplorer
Title: GUI to Explore Stable Isotope Data Files
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Sebastian", "Kopf", , "seb.kopf@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a graphical user interface to explore stable isotope data files using the isoreader2 package, including browsing, visualizing, and exporting isotope data.
